uk.ac.ebi.kraken.interfaces.uniprot.citationsNew

Interface Citation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasEvidences, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Book, ElectronicArticle, JournalArticle, Patent, Submission, Thesis, UnpublishedJournalArticle, UnpublishedObservations

    public interface Citation
extends Serializable, HasEvidences
    The basic type containing the common values that are present in each and every Citation

    In the flatfile this is the Rx lines

    To build a citation for use in you program @link uk.ac.ebi.kraken.interfaces.factories.DefaultCitationFactory

        List<EvidenceId> getEvidenceIds()
        Description copied from interface: HasEvidences
        Returns the EvidenceIds of the EvidenceTagable object.

        These values can be found in the many lines of the flat file. Some examples are marked in the following example. 
         ...
 ID   Q8J030      PRELIMINARY;      PRT;   669 AA.
 AC   Q8J030;
 DT   01-MAR-2003 (TrEMBLrel. 23, Created)
 DT   01-MAR-2003 (TrEMBLrel. 23, Last sequence update)
 DT   01-MAR-2003 (TrEMBLrel. 23, Last annotation update)
 DE   Galactosylceramidase (Krabbe disease){EI1,EP2}.
 OS   Homo sapiens (Human).
 OC   Eukaryota; Metazoa; Chordata; Craniata; Vertebrata; Euteleostomi;
 OC   Mammalia; Eutheria; Primates; Catarrhini; Hominidae; Homo.
 OX   NCBI_TaxID=9606{EP2};
 RN   [1]{EI1}
 RP   SEQUENCE FROM N.A.
 RC   TISSUE=Testis;
 RA   Strausberg R.;
 RL   Submitted (AUG-2002) to the EMBL/GenBank/DDBJ databases.
 DR   EMBL; BC036518; AAH36518.1; -.{EI1}
 ...
